const experienceData = [
    {
        id: 1,
        date: "April 2024 - Present",
        company: "McMaster University - ChemAI Lab",
        title: "Machine Learning Researcher",
        description: `description.`,
        logo: 'https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/5/53/McMaster_University_logo.svg'
    },
    {
        id: 2,
        date: "May 2023 - August 2023",
        company: "VACS Ltd.",
        title: "Calibration Engineer Intern",
        description: `Leveraging Microsoft Azure services, including 
        Power Platform and Logic Apps, scalable solutions were created and 
        implemented to improve system efficiency and business processes. 
        This involved applying advanced programming concepts to optimize 
        backend functionality and data processing workflows. Additionally, 
        PowerShell was utilized to troubleshoot and resolve system-level 
        issues in applications hosted on Azure, as well as to develop robust 
        scripts for automating tasks, thereby streamlining system processes 
        and enhancing efficiency within the Azure environment.`,
        logo: 'https://vacs.calibrations.ca/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/VacsCalLogo.png'
    },
    {
        id: 3,
        date: "Graduation Expected May 2027",
        company: "University of Toronto",
        title: "Bachelor of Applied Science in Engineering Science majoring in Machine Intelligence",
        description: `Relevant Coursework: Machine Learning, Data Structures and Algorithms, Natural Language Computing, Computational Linguistics`,
        logo: 'https://maplelab.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/UofTlogo.png'
    }
    // Add more experiences here
];

export default experienceData;
